ZH: 她在海滩上划小船。
EN: She is rowing a small boat on the beach.

ZH: 他划着划艇来到了对岸。
EN: He paddled the kayak to the other side.

ZH: 我喜欢在湖上划船。
EN: I enjoy rowing on the lake.

ZH: 小姐姐用力地划了几下，停了下来。
EN: The young lady rowed hard for a few strokes and then stopped.

ZH: 别忘了划艇时要注意安全。
EN: Don't forget to pay attention to safety when paddling a kayak.

ZH: 爸爸教我如何划皮划艇。
EN: Dad taught me how to row a kayak.

ZH: 别人划快艇兜风的时候，我在岸上晒太阳。
EN: While others were speeding around on jet skis, I was sunbathing on the shore.

ZH: 我在海边划着一只小舢板。
EN: I was rowing a small canoe by the seaside.

ZH: 他在湖上划船散心。
EN: He rows on the lake to relax.

ZH: 我们可以租一只划艇在湖上划一圈。
EN: We can rent a kayak to row around the lake.

ZH: 玛丽每周都会去划艇锻炼。
EN: Mary goes kayaking every week for exercise.

ZH: 很多人在周末来这里划皮划艇。
EN: Many people come here on weekends to row kayaks.

ZH: 划船的感觉真是太棒了。
EN: Rowing a boat feels really great.

ZH: 昨天他们去河边划船了。
EN: They went rowing by the river yesterday.

ZH: 我想约几个朋友一起去划船。
EN: I want to invite a few friends to go rowing together.

ZH: 女孩子们在湖上享受着划皮划艇的乐趣。
EN: The girls are enjoying the fun of kayaking on the lake.

ZH: 划艇是我最喜欢的水上活动之一。
EN: Kayaking is one of my favorite water activities.

ZH: 他划着桨穿梭在繁忙的水道中。
EN: He paddled through the busy waterway.

ZH: 小孩子学习划皮划艇时需要专业指导。
EN: Children need professional guidance when learning to kayak.

ZH: 我喜欢沉浸在划船的快乐中。
EN: I enjoy immersing myself in the joy of rowing.
